        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "the diff get and diff obtain is behaving differently with linematch enabled because the diffs blocks are broken up into more granular pieces. I believe to get the behavior that you are expecting, you need to highlight the whole area you want to modify and then type  :diffget while in visual line mode\n@chrisbra \nwhether or not to break the diffs into smaller hunks was a topic of discussion:\nhttps://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/14537#issuecomment-1025699032\nhttps://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/14537#issuecomment-1052285602",
